nodes.text: Headache Bar was a seedy cantina, located on level 20 of Nar Shaddaa. During the reign of the Galactic Empire, tempest spice was funneled through the bar by the clientele. Known for being poorly lit, something that suited the intoxicated an inebriate patrons well; it was rumored that around the clock, one of the apparently unconscious beings slumped at a table was actually dead.
